		@@.notmc-speech; Well, yeah, of course...@@<br>
		@@.mc-speech; Alright, let's continue.@@<br>
	<<elseif $companion.name eq "Alex" or $companion.name eq "Taylor" or $companion.name eq "Casey">>
		@@.mc-thoughts; You enter and see the ghost defiling $companion.name, taking every opportunity to satisfy its desires. Its touches and actions make $companion.name moan, sending him into a spiral of wild ecstasy and taboo pleasure.<br>
